%A1nh-T%C3%B4ng/Nguy%E1%BB%87t-h%E1%BA%A1-tu%C3%BD-%E1%BA%A9m/poem-_ycWhllqhhkLejeMAYlkRg">Nguyệt hạ tuý ẩm - 月下醉飲</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%AA-Th%C3%A1nh-T%C3%B4ng/author-FSJg5-ivZkPUR1nhJkA6Fg">Lê Thánh Tông</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%C3%A0n-S%C6%A1n/Thi%C3%AAn-ni%C3%AAn-th%E1%BA%A1ch-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-c%E1%BB%95-nh%C3%A2n-tung/poem-p5CiCdUSZM094mZ7SNas8Q">Thiên niên thạch thượng cổ nhân tung - 千年石上古人蹤</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%C3%A0n-S%C6%A1n/author-o98HuijKnTRKdgvHyXbEYw">Hàn Sơn</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%C3%AAn-Hi%E1%BA%BFu-V%E1%BA%A5n/Thu-d%E1%BA%A1/poem-nJvwRGHERPCLC7-XSffS1w">Thu dạ - 秋夜</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%C3%AAn-Hi%E1%BA%BFu-V%E1%BA%A5n/author-lCIs61Hzjl6rqKSiwGq6ow">Nguyên Hiếu Vấn</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Nh%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3c-H%C6%B0/Xu%C3%A2n-giang-hoa-nguy%E1%BB%87t-d%E1%BA%A1/poem-Ig1Xj0OA8zR8Kmy66SA-FQ">Xuân giang hoa nguyệt dạ - 春江花月夜</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Nh%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3c-H%C6%B0/author-U0M-4XTJEfTnLrqsmVsoXQ">Trương Nhược Hư</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
